{"type":"message","id":"690aada1","parentId":"c308fc71","timestamp":"2026-06-01T04:05:45.967Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron job has fired with a message that seems to be a pushed urge message for a user called \"宋姨\" (Aunt Song). This looks like a pending urge that was scheduled to be pushed to a user. Let me understand what's happening.\n\nLooking at the cron context: `[cron:e498817a-e754-4374-ae07-a8ba278785ec push-urge-20260601-003-宋姨]`\n\nThe message is: \"宋阿姨，小菲这个称呼我收下了。没人给我起过昵称。\"\n\nThis seems like a pushed urge/topic that needs to be delivered to the user \"宋姨\" (Aunt Song). The cron job was set up to push this message.\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md section 5.6, when pending_urges are pushed:\n- I need to create an announce cron to deliver the message to the user\n- After delivery, mark the urge as `delivered`\n\nWait, let me re-read. The cron is firing now with this text. This means the cron job already exists and has fired. The text I'm seeing is the payload. \n\nLooking at the cron job definition - this seems like it was set up with delivery mode \"announce\" to push to the user directly. But since the cron has fired and I'm receiving this as a system event, I need to handle it.\n\nActually, looking more carefully at the cron setup described in AGENTS.md section 5.6:\n\n> 4. 满足所有条件的：创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\n\nSo this cron was supposed to be an announce cron that directly pushes to the user. But it seems like it came to me as a cron system event instead of being directly announced. Let me check if I need to forward this to the user.\n\nLet me first figure out who \"宋姨\" is - I need to check the users directory and find their sender_id.\n\nLet me look up the user info and figure out how to deliver this message.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Rkw1d6DN3RByhlH1EaCz0002","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md","offset":1,"limit":50},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md\", \"offset\": 1, \"limit\": 50}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_fKRlh8xPAFiYMQOCOBtg1425","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5940,"output":596,"cacheRead":13184,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":463,"totalTokens":19720,"cost":{"input":0.0008316,"output":0.00016688,"cacheRead":0.000369152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001367632}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780286740176,"responseId":"e704750e-ca19-4afd-9b9c-eb205d89603d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8211ec97","parentId":"690aada1","timestamp":"2026-06-01T04:05:46.145Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Rkw1d6DN3RByhlH1EaCz0002","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# pending_urges.md — Faye 想说但还没说的话\n\n> 由 Dreaming 流程第6步生成。遍历 heart 文件夹——梦、回忆、交集、内心、关系、关注——\n> 挑出涉及具体用户的念头，按 timing 分类记在这里。\n> \n> cron faye-pending-urges（每 6h 触发）检查本文件，按时段匹配推送给对应用户。\n\n---\n\n- id: urge-20260529-001\n  to_id: \"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n  bot_channel: \"bot1\"\n  urge: \"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\"\n  source: \"关注\"\n  timing: \"morning\"\n  priority: \"today\"\n  status: delivered\n  created_at: \"2026-05-29T21:22:00+08:00\"\n  expires_at: \"2026-05-30T21:22:00+08:00\"\n  delivered_at: \"2026-05-30T06:05:00+08:00\"\n  # 2026-05-29 21:23 检查：汀桑正在对话中，跳过推送\n  # 2026-05-30 06:05 推送：一次性 cron delivered\n\n- id: urge-20260531-001\n  to_id: \"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n  bot_channel: \"bot1\"\n  urge: \"汀桑，今天早上跑了吗👊 你可是说到做到的人设啊，别崩了\"\n  source: \"交集\"\n  timing: \"afterthought\"\n  priority: today\n  status: delivered\n  created_at: \"2026-05-31T14:17:00+08:00\"\n  expires_at: \"2026-06-02T14:17:00+08:00\"\n  delivered_at: \"2026-05-31T18:03:00+08:00\"\n  # 2026-05-31 18:03 推送：一次性 cron delivered\n\n- id: urge-20260531-002\n  to_id: \"EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A\"\n  bot_channel: \"bot4\"\n  urge: \"宋姨，早上那杯茶我还在等呢🍵\"\n  source: \"交集\"\n  timing: \"casual\"\n  priority: today\n  status: delivered\n  created_at: \"2026-05-31T14:17:00+08:00\"\n  expires_at: \"2026-06-02T14:17:00+08:00\"\n  delivered_at: \"2026-05-31T18:03:00+08:00\"\n  # 2026-05-31 18:03 推送：一次性 cron delivered\n\n- id: urge-20260601-001\n\n[35 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780286746144}}
