{"type":"message","id":"3a4171da","parentId":"8068b5f5","timestamp":"2026-06-01T04:05:54.666Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so this is urge-20260601-003 for user 宋志红 (to_id: EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A) via bot4. The urge text is: \"宋阿姨，小菲这个称呼我收下了。没人给我起过昵称。\"\n\nThe cron has fired and sent this as a system event to me (the father session). According to the setup in AGENTS.md 5.6, this should have been set up as an announce cron that directly pushes to the user. But instead it came to me as a system event.\n\nLet me check - this cron job was set up with what session target? Looking at the cron activation `[cron:e498817a-e754-4374-ae07-a8ba278785ec push-urge-20260601-003-宋姨]` - it seems like it came to the main session as a system event.\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md 5.6 step 4:\n> 4. 满足所有条件的：创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\n\nSo this should have been an announce directly to the user. But it arrived here. I need to forward this to the user through bot4 (QQ channel).\n\nLet me send this message to the user through the appropriate channel. Since the delivery is supposed to be through a QQ bot announce, I need to check if I can use the announce delivery mechanism.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully - the cron job might have been configured as an \"agentTurn\" to the current session (my session), which means it's giving me the task to actually send the message. Let me just forward it.\n\nLet me send the message to user 宋志红. Since the urge specifies bot_channel: \"bot4\", I need to deliver through bot4.\n\nBut I don't have a direct \"send message\" tool. The delivery mechanism described uses announce cron. Let me create a one-time announce cron to push this message instead.\n\nActually wait - I should mark the urge as delivered after sending. Let me first send the message, then update the pending_urges.md.\n\nSince the cron came to me (the Father session), I think the intent is for me to now forward this message to the user. Let me create an announce cron to push it.\n\nActually, looking at the cron setup more carefully: I can use the cron tool to add a job with delivery.mode=announce. Let me do that.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"This is urge-20260601-003 for 宋姨. The cron delivered it to me instead of announcing directly. Let me push it out."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_7ty3xRTrTVeTba7LqyDU6403","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"push-urge-20260601-003-宋姨-deliver","schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-06-01T04:06:00Z"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[announce] 宋阿姨，小菲这个称呼我收下了。没人给我起过昵称。"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot4","to":"qqbot:c2c:EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","deleteAfterRun":true,"description":"推送 urge-20260601-003 给宋姨"}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\":\"push-urge-20260601-003-宋姨-deliver\",\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"at\",\"at\":\"2026-06-01T04:06:00Z\"},\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"[announce] 宋阿姨，小菲这个称呼我收下了。没人给我起过昵称。\"},\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\",\"channel\":\"qqbot\",\"accountId\":\"bot4\",\"to\":\"qqbot:c2c:EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A\"},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"deleteAfterRun\":true,\"description\":\"推送 urge-20260601-003 给宋姨\"}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":715,"output":798,"cacheRead":20736,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":561,"totalTokens":22249,"cost":{"input":0.00010010000000000001,"output":0.00022344000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000580608,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000904148}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780286748586,"responseId":"c07676b4-14fc-44d2-bd57-3bbae587306f"}}
